              <p class="text-sm mb-2">Typical range: £15-£50/month/device</p>
              <p class="text-sm">Fixed cost regardless of turnover. Multi-device operations face significant multiplication effect.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="highlight-box">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Authorisation Fees</h4>
              <p class="text-sm mb-2">Typical range: 1p-5p/transaction</p>
              <p class="text-sm">Very high impact for low-value, high-count merchants. Cumulative and rarely in headline comparison.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="highlight-box">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Minimum Monthly Service Charge</h4>
              <p class="text-sm mb-2">Typical range: £10-£50/month</p>
              <p class="text-sm">Extreme impact for low/seasonal volume. Guarantees provider revenue regardless of activity.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="highlight-box">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Chargeback Fees</h4>
              <p class="text-sm mb-2">Typical range: £15-£25/dispute + goods loss</p>
              <p class="text-sm">Variable impact; potentially catastrophic at high rates. Friendly fraud growth makes unpredictable.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
